<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-blue-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-200 to-blue-300 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center text-blue-900">
            <div class="text-8xl mb-4">👨‍⚕️</div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Dr. James Mitchell</p>
            <p class="text-sm">Founder, Heart Health Method</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <p class="text-lg text-blue-600 font-medium mb-2">Hi, I'm Dr. James</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">I created this because I was tired of seeing patients struggle</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
          After years of prescribing the same medications and watching patients cycle through the same struggles, I knew there had to be a better way.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
          I dove into the research—nutritional science, lifestyle medicine, behavioral psychology. What I discovered changed everything: most cardiovascular disease is preventable and even reversible through targeted lifestyle interventions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">
          With guidance from colleagues at Stanford, Harvard, and Johns Hopkins, plus my own clinical experience with 5,000+ patients, I created the Heart Health Method.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Now I'm honored to share it with you, so you can get the healthy, energetic life you deserve without depending on pills.
        </p>
        <div class="text-gray-900">
          <p class="font-semibold">Warmly,</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-xl">Dr. James Mitchell</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Founder of Heart Health Method</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Board-Certified Cardiologist, 15+ Years Clinical Experience</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
